query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN importado_de = 'google_calendar' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as importados_google,
  COUNT(DISTINCT convenio) as convenios,
  COUNT(DISTINCT paciente_nome) as pacientes_unicos
FROM agendamentos;
